title: Ruslan Zyazikov
text:
Ruslan Magametaliyevich Zyazikov (; born 13 December 1984) is a Russian former professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He played in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Angusht%20Nazran">FC Angusht Nazran</a> in the 2013–14 season.
